      "description": "Join millions of players worldwide in the most played Solitaire game in history - now featuring MORE great games to play!\n\nEnjoy classic Solitaire game modes everyone loves - Klondike Solitaire, Spider Solitaire, FreeCell Solitaire, TriPeaks Solitaire & Pyramid Solitaire. Keep your mind sharp increasing Difficulty, completing Daily Challenges, playing Weekly Rewards, or climbing the leaderboard in Events. \n\nCelebrate WINS by leveling up with XP, collecting Trophies, Achievements & MORE! Plus, discover other great match-3, arcade and puzzle games ready to play anytime - Microsoft Bubble, Jewel, Gravity Blocks, Gem Drop & Mahjong 3D.\n\nSign in with a Microsoft or Xbox Account to save your progress, collect awards and play across devices.\nWith so much to play, Microsoft Solitaire Collection is the perfect app for anyone.\n\nFeatures:\n• 5 favorite Solitaire game modes\n• 5 NEW Challenges every day\n• Choose your Difficulty\n• Weekly Rewards, Events & Achievements\n• MORE great games ready to play inside\n\nBecome a Premium Member\n• Play Ad-FREE\n• Collect XP (win or lose)\n• Daily Challenges: 2x points & access to past Challenges\n• Unlimited use of Solitaire Solver\n• Special boosts in Endless TriPeaks & Pyramid \n• Extra bonuses in other games \n• FREE Retro bundle & Xbox card backs\n\nSolitaire Premium is available for mobile only. Non-transferrable to other platforms.\nPayment will be charged to your iTunes Account on confirmation of purchase. Subscription automatically renews monthly or annually depending on the subscription type purchased. Payment will be charged to your iTunes Account within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period. Turn off auto-renewal by going to your Account Settings after purchase. If auto-renewal is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period, you will not be charged for the next period. All cancellations will take effect at the end of the current period.\n\nFor more information visit: https://aka.ms/microsoftsolitaire_support\n\n© Microsoft 2025. All Rights Reserved. Microsoft, Microsoft Casual Games, the product logos and Microsoft Solitaire Collection, and the Microsoft Solitaire Collection logos are trademarks of the Microsoft group of companies. All other trademarks are the property of their respective owners. Acceptance of Microsoft Services Agreement and Privacy Statement are required to play. (https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/servicesagreement, https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/privacy/privacystatement) Microsoft account registration required for cross-platform play. Game offers in-app purchases. Persistent internet connection required. Features, online services and system requirements may vary by country and are subject to change or retirement over time.",
